descriptionHtml:
Hi everybody,

A preset for Nordic women but you can use for another human races.

[u][b]How to install it ?[/b][/u]

Data ==> SKSE ==> Plugins ==> CharGen ==> Presets

Use [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?]RaceMenu[/url] During character creation (or using "showracemenu" command with the
console) go to "Presets", press F9, select my preset and it's done !

I'm using my Bodyslide preset ([url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70082/?]Slim to Busty[/url]), [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/70834/?]Demoniac- 4K Texture Package Based on Realgirl n SG[/url]

The hair is KS Hairdos Renewal (found in Nexus).
author: Thezibaim
